332
00:20:20,583 --> 00:20:22,791
Chen Jing'an, calm down, don't be impulsive.

333
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:25,375
Let's take our time to discuss the transfer.

334
00:20:25,375 --> 00:20:26,375
