370
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,875
I'll go now.

371
00:21:44,166 --> 00:21:44,625
Okay.

372
00:21:44,625 --> 00:21:45,166
Go ahead.

373
00:21:51,666 --> 00:21:52,791
Soul swap...

374
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:55,750
This kid is

375
00:21:55,958 --> 00:21:57,500
