400
00:26:30,250 --> 00:26:32,000
You and Dad can check my answers.

401
00:26:32,041 --> 00:26:32,708
Then you'll see

402
00:26:32,708 --> 00:26:34,041
I'm not bad at physics at all.

403
00:26:34,041 --> 00:26:35,625
I can totally switch to science.

404
00:26:36,416 --> 00:26:37,583
Do it later.

405
00:26:37,583 --> 00:26:39,333
