410
00:26:51,958 --> 00:26:52,958
You can check them.

411
00:26:54,291 --> 00:26:55,125
I'm going to eat first.

412
00:27:11,166 --> 00:27:11,958
I didn't expect

413
00:27:12,666 --> 00:27:13,791
